rows.label: tlk43310191_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Invidia and Superbia are in close
proximity around this period, and
Temperantia is slap bang in the middle.

rows.label: tlk43310191_02_msg0003
rows.name:
It's established as a buffer zone
where all combat is prohibited.

rows.label: tlk43310191_02_msg0004
rows.name:
But both sides station forces there
in case something does break out.

rows.label: tlk43310191_02_msg0005
rows.name:
That's why we're stocking this ship up
with rations and soldiers and heading
to Temperantia right now.
